item.title: Map Kochi
item.description: We mapped Kochin on Collector’s request. It was a great success. Happy Birthday @openstreetmap Project. Its Sweet 16 ❤️ My small gift to #Covid19 Warriors and #OSMKerala Community. Ward Delimitation Map of Kochi Corporation, Kerala. Thanks @snehil0802 @naveenpf @BodhishThomas @Muzirian & all Community @osm_in #KochiMap #KeralaMaps #EnteKochi pic.twitter.com/uYiY0zLsHQ — Manoj Karingamadathil (@manojkmohan) August 8, 2020
